). FWL 9.1 mm , WLR 0.26. Vertex straw-yellow, with sparse brown scales; frons glossy golden. PLB 1.0 × vertical eye diameter, straw-yellow, tip light brown. Proboscis light brown. Eyes not enlarged; interocular index 0.4. Antenna 3.3 × FWL, with simple inwardly directed pegs. Scape and proximal third of flagellum dark brown, with bronze luster; then colour of flagellum gradually changes to light grey. Tegulae and thorax coppery brown; dorsum marginally with bands of yellow scales. Forewing (
